% fztoolz, ansible, automation, devops

# Run an Ansible playbook with interactive selection
; Lets you select:
; 1. Playbook from 'playbooks/' directory
; 2. Inventory file (optional)
; 3. Hosts/groups (optional)
; 4. Tags (optional)
; 
; Builds and prints the full ansible-playbook command for you
aplay

# Run an Ansible role with interactive selection  
; Interactive workflow to run a standalone Ansible role:
; 1. Select role from 'roles/' directory
; 2. Choose inventory file (optional)
; 3. Pick target hosts (optional)
; 4. Select tags to apply (optional)
;
; Builds and prints a full ansible command with include_role
arole
